::Aerotaur::
       He lurches forward as the explosions quake through the mountain.  He 
sighs.  "I thought they had left."  He glances at the screen and waits for 
the second blast (the grenade) to shake the base.  He shakes his head and 
walks to the door.  He goes outside just far enough to get one shot off 
before he runs back inside.  He fires his one shot at the ground under the 
group, thus collapsing the ground under them a few feet due to the pit 
Terrataur had dug earlier.  He walks back inside to Nightlight.  "That should 
take them a little while to get out of.  We need to have a meeting.

--part1_12b.c4ba31c.299c8474_boundary
